entries.task00_comm_message_text: Some of the ventillation shafts are blocked. I hate to think of how. You will need to shut them manually. Give me a few moments and I'll send you the vent waypoints.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Look, I don't know you but you are literally our only hope for stopping the virus. I need you to go to those locations and shut the vents off manually.
